    <a href="/high-net-worth" class="drawer-link">High-Net-Worth Individuals <span class="drawer-link-arrow">&#8250;</span></a>
    <a href="/professionals" class="drawer-link">For Professionals <span class="drawer-link-arrow">&#8250;</span></a>
    <div class="drawer-section-label">About</div>
    <a href="/about/mckay-tucker" class="drawer-link">J. McKay Tucker, Esq. <span class="drawer-link-arrow">&#8250;</span></a>
    <a href="/about/jay-allen" class="drawer-link">Jay Allen, Esq. <span class="drawer-link-arrow">&#8250;</span></a>
    <a href="/about" class="drawer-link">Our Process <span class="drawer-link-arrow">&#8250;</span></a>
    <a href="/contact" class="drawer-cta">Book Free Consultation</a>
    <a href="tel:4800000000" class="drawer-phone">(480) 000-0000</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <main>
    <slot />
  </main>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <span class="footer-logo-name">Mesa Estate Planning</span>
        <span class="footer-logo-sub">Attorney at Law &middot; Mesa, AZ</span>
        <p>Helping Mesa families and business owners protect what matters most — with expert legal counsel and personal attention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-cols">
        <div class="footer-col"><h4>Services</h4><ul><li><a href="/services/wills-and-trusts">Wills &amp; Trusts</a></li><li><a href="/services/financial-power-of-attorney">Powers of Attorney</a></li><li><a href="/services/business-succession-planning">Business Succession</a></li><li><a href="/services/asset-protection">Asset Protection</a></li><li><a href="/services/estate-tax-planning">Estate Tax Planning</a></li></ul></div>
        <div class="footer-col"><h4>Who We Serve</h4><ul><li><a href="/families">Families &amp; Parents</a></li><li><a href="/business-owners">Business Owners</a></li><li><a href="/high-net-worth">High-Net-Worth</a></li><li><a href="/professionals">For Professionals</a></li></ul></div>
        <div class="footer-col"><h4>Resources</h4><ul><li><a href="/blog">Articles &amp; Guides</a></li><li><a href="/tools">Free Tools</a></li><li><a href="/downloads">Checklists</a></li><li><a href="/blog?filter=case-studies">Case Studies</a></li></ul></div>
        <div class="footer-col"><h4>Firm</h4><ul><li><a href="/about/mckay-tucker">J. McKay Tucker, Esq.</a></li><li><a href="/about/jay-allen">Jay Allen, Esq.</a></li><li><a href="/about">Our Process</a></li><li><a href="tel:4800000000">(480) 000-0000</a></li><li><a href="mailto:info@mesaestateplanninglawyers.com">info@mesaestateplanninglawyers.com</a></li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
